[{"id":"569225eb0d504f27ad6eb603bda3f644","from":"Robin Hood","from_email":"robinhood@robinhood.org","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"What a Night!","date":"2015-05-13T14:40:48.000Z","formatted_date":"May 13, 2015","formatted_time":"2:40 PM","body":"To view this email as a web page, go to the link below, or copy and paste it into your browser's address window.\nhttp://view.s6.exacttarget.com/?j=fec5167076610c75&m=fe9312727666077e7c&ls=fe301771706c057c741c73&l=ff2613717d6d&s=fe5e1076766d027d7511&jb=ffcf14&ju=\n\nThank you so much for joining us last night at the Javits center as you and thousands of others came together to create a true community of caring. We are truly humbled by the generosity of our supporters, who contributed $101,688,198, every penny of which will fund programs that have the power to lift tens of thousands of New Yorkers out of poverty.\n\nhttp://www.robinhood.org/bb15?amount=0&linkid= \nCOMPLETE YOUR PLEDGE \u00bb\n\nIf you made a pledge last night--thank you. If you would like to fulfill your donation online please \nhttp://www.robinhood.org/bb15?amount=0&linkid= \nclick here, or you can call 212-844-3583 and a member of the Robin Hood team will assist you.\nIf you did not make a pledge last night but would like to do so, please call us at the number above.\n\nhttp://www.robinhood.org/sites/default/files/user-uploaded-images/RH_Benefit_2015.jpeg \nTogether we are Robin Hood!\n\nTHANK YOU FOR BEING ROBIN HOOD.\n\nROBIN HOOD\nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/RobinHoodNYC \n\nhttp://instagram.com/robinhoodnyc \n\nhttp://robinhoodnyc.tumblr.com/ \n\nhttp://twitter.com/robinhoodnyc \n\nhttp://www.facebook.com/robinhood \n826 Broadway, 9th Floor\nNew York, NY 10003, USA\n212-227-6601 | \nhttp://www.robinhood.org/ \nrobinhood.org\nhttp://cl.s6.exct.net/profile_center.aspx?s=fe5e1076766d027d7511&mid=fe9312727666077e7c&j=fec5167076610c75&l=ff2613717d6d&jb=ffcf14&ju